swift/container/reconciler.py.message:
This except is catching more then just an unhandled exception (Exception) but a Timeout as well. Seeing as we are logging the unhandled exception, with out giving any information on it, should be also log if it was a timeout, to aid in debudding? 

    try:
        return self.reconcile()
    except Exception:
        self.logger.exception('Unhandled Exception trying to reconcile')
    except Timeout:
        self.logger.exception('Timeout reached while trying to reconcile')
    finally:
        self.log_stats(force=True)

Or even log a hint to what the unhandled exception was in relation to?

